race.description: Happy 16th Wedding Anniversary Luke & Emma Hcp
race.comment: The stayers round out the card. LIKEABEEL (2) was a bit plain at the latest effort but go on the solid win around this circuit two back. Has placed two from three over this distance range and should be right there at the business end. KENSHIN MARU (4) has a solid record here on his home circuit with a win and three seconds from nine starts. Gets 2kg off with the claim and can make his presence felt. JIMMY NAILS (6) is a last-start Lismore winner who will be high on confidence now. Top-three candidate. AMALGAMATION (5) is a bit hit or miss but placed in town last time out and can feature with a repeat of that performance. KALAMIA KING (10) is still a maiden but may earn some minor money.
